  <title translate="true">Как проверить данные перед сохранением задачи (Before Task Edit Trigger)</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Как проверить данные перед сохранением задачи (Before Task Edit Trigger)</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:16px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666;" translate="true">Чтобы проверять данные перед сохранением существующей задачи, нужно подключить к ее процессу триггер Before Edit Task.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666;" translate="true">Он должен соответствовать интерфейсу</text><text styleclass="apple-converted-space" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666;" translate="true">com.trackstudio.external.TaskTrigger</text><text styleclass="apple-converted-space" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666;" translate="true">и располагаться в папке</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal_workflow" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:16px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffcc; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; padding:8px; border-color:#606060; border-style:single; border-width:1px; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="workflow" style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">./etc/plugins/scripts/before_edit_task/</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:16px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666;" translate="true">Ниже пример триггера, который проверяет, указан ли для задачи правильный deadline. Для того, чтобы указать пользователю на ошибку и не сохранять задачу, мы выбрасываем в триггере UserException. При этом пользователь возвращается на страницу редактирования задачи. Данные остаются введенными.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example_workflow" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:16px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffcc; white-space:nowrap; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; padding:8px; border-color:#606060; border-style:single; border-width:1px; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="workflow" style="font-family:&apos;Courier New&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">package scripts.before_edit_task;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example_workflow" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffcc; white-space:nowrap; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; padding:8px; border-color:#606060; border-style:single; border-width:1px; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="workflow" style="font-family:&apos;Courier New&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">import com.trackstudio.exception.GranException;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example_workflow" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffcc; white-space:nowrap; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; padding:8px; border-color:#606060; border-style:single; border-width:1px; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="workflow" style="font-family:&apos;Courier New&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">import com.trackstudio.exception.UserException;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example_workflow" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffcc; white-space:nowrap; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; padding:8px; border-color:#606060; border-style:single; border-width:1px; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="workflow" style="font-family:&apos;Courier New&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">import com.trackstudio.external.TaskTrigger;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example_workflow" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffcc; white-space:nowrap; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; padding:8px; border-color:#606060; border-style:single; border-width:1px; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="workflow" style="font-family:&apos;Courier New&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">import com.trackstudio.secured.SecuredTaskTriggerBean;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example_workflow" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffcc; white-space:nowrap; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; padding:8px; border-color:#606060; border-style:single; border-width:1px; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="workflow" style="font-family:&apos;Courier New&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">import java.util.Calendar;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example_workflow" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffcc; white-space:nowrap; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; padding:8px; border-color:#606060; border-style:single; border-width:1px; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="workflow" style="font-family:&apos;Courier New&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">public class CheckDeadline implements TaskTrigger {</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example_workflow" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffcc; white-space:nowrap; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; padding:8px; border-color:#606060; border-style:single; border-width:1px; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="workflow" style="font-family:&apos;Courier New&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;public SecuredTaskTriggerBean execute(SecuredTaskTriggerBean securedTaskTriggerBean) throws GranException {</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example_workflow" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffcc; white-space:nowrap; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; padding:8px; border-color:#606060; border-style:single; border-width:1px; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="workflow" style="font-family:&apos;Courier New&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;Calendar deadline = securedTaskTriggerBean.getDeadline();</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example_workflow" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffcc; white-space:nowrap; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; padding:8px; border-color:#606060; border-style:single; border-width:1px; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="workflow" style="font-family:&apos;Courier New&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;Calendar now = Calendar.getInstance();</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example_workflow" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffcc; white-space:nowrap; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; padding:8px; border-color:#606060; border-style:single; border-width:1px; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="workflow" style="font-family:&apos;Courier New&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;if (deadline == null || deadline.before(now)) throw new UserException(&quot;Укажите срок выполнения задачи&quot;);</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example_workflow" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffcc; white-space:nowrap; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; padding:8px; border-color:#606060; border-style:single; border-width:1px; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="workflow" style="font-family:&apos;Courier New&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;return securedTaskTriggerBean;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example_workflow" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffcc; white-space:nowrap; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; padding:8px; border-color:#606060; border-style:single; border-width:1px; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="workflow" style="font-family:&apos;Courier New&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;}</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example_workflow" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffcc; white-space:nowrap; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; padding:8px; border-color:#606060; border-style:single; border-width:1px; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="workflow" style="font-family:&apos;Courier New&apos;; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;" translate="true">}</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:16px; line-height:1.0; background-color:#ffffff; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Verdana; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#666666;" translate="true">С помощью триггеров Before Edit Task обычно выполняются действия, которые необходимо совершить до сохранения задачи, так, чтобы если эти действия завершились неуспешно, пользователь вернулся на страницу ввода и мог повторить действия.</text></para>
